data.description: Welcome home to this lovely traditional style, 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home located in sought-after Snellville. This stunning brick-front boasts plenty of living space, both indoor and outdoor. Your main level features a sitting room which leads to the open concept kitchen/living, formal dining room, and breakfast area. Solid wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops with bar seating making this the kitchen of your dreams! The spacious family room features a corner fireplace and a view to your sprawling backyard perfect for inside/outside entertainment. Upstairs features a very spacious loft/den, 2 secondary bedrooms, a bathroom and an owner's suite with an oversized walk-in closet, luxurious en-suite bathroom with separate shower/tub and a double vanity set up. Step outside to your expansive backyard, perfect for all weather entertainment – includes a covered front and back screened in porch. Enjoy your morning cup of coffee on the front or back porch, while watching the sunrise. Conveniently located near Norris Lake, local restaurants and easy access to shopping, entertainment, and schools. This home is a true gem-you don't want to miss it!
